long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ignite your new tab with the vibrant energy of a BMW with Neon Lights! This Chrome extension transforms your browser into a stunning showcase of automotive brilliance.

The BMW with Neon Lights live wallpaper extension highlights the sleek design of this iconic car, illuminated by striking neon hues. This eye-catching visual experience enhances your browsing while integrating essential tools for seamless navigation.

Easily search the web with the Google search bar, customize shortcuts to your favorite sites, and keep track of time with a convenient clock-date display.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper featuring a BMW adorned with neon lights
Google Search Bar for fast and easy browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for your top websites
Clock-Date display to stay organized

Transform your new tab into a high-octane experience with the allure of a BMW with Neon Lights! For more exciting wallpapers, visit Gameograf.com to discover additional automotive themes.
